# Rock Paper Scissors Game (Python)

## Description
This is a simple Rock-Paper-Scissors game developed using Python where the user plays against the computer.

## Features
- User input
- Random computer choice
- Game result detection
- Score tracking
- Multiple rounds

## Technologies Used
- Python
- Random module

## How to Run

1. Install Python
2. Run the program

python rock_paper_scissors.py

## Game Rules

Rock beats Scissors  
Scissors beat Paper  
Paper beats Rock  

